EU Says ‘Fully Coordinated Approach’ Needed on Recapitalizations

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-10-11T10:55:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/eu-says-fully-coordinated-approach-needed-on-recapitalizations.html
The European Union said a “fully
coordinated approach” is needed on bank recapitalizations
across the region and that an EU proposal on the subject are not
yet ready.  The European Commission, the EU executive in Brussels, will
present its recapitalization proposal once it is ready, Pia
Ahrenkilde-Hansen, a spokeswoman for the EU, told reporters
today in Brussels.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jones Hayden at 
 jhayden1@bloomberg.net  